  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n_opening in repo as not sure if bug or missing feature_\r\n\r\nWhen pasting  large message to send. The message gets truncated with no feedback to the user.\r\nMeaning that one can send a truncated message without realising it.\r\n\r\nA better UX (in my opinion) is to let the full message being pasted in the box but have the character counter display a negative value and disable the ability to send until the character counter value hits zero.\r\n\r\nVersion: 0.13.2\r\n\r\n",
